## DropErc721Contract.getAllClaimed() method

Get All Claimed NFTs

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
getAllClaimed(queryParams?: QueryAllParams): Promise<NFTMetadataOwner[]>;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  queryParams | QueryAllParams | optional filtering to only fetch a subset of results. |

<b>Returns:</b>

Promise&lt;NFTMetadataOwner\[\]&gt;

The NFT metadata and their ownersfor all NFTs queried.

## Remarks

Fetch all the NFTs (and their owners) that have been claimed in this Drop.

\*

## Example


